quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  111,1,"Perish the two hands of Abu Lahab (an uncle of the Prophet), and perish he"
  111,2,His wealth and his children (etc.) will not benefit him
  111,3,He will be burnt in a Fire of blazing flames
  111,4,"And his wife too, who carries wood (thorns of Sadan which she used to put on the way of the Prophet (Peace be upon him), or use to slander him"
  111,5,In her neck is a twisted rope of Masad (palm fibre)